***************************WELCOME TO GIT CHALLENGE**********************

Task1:
1)create a directory "gitc1" on desktop
2)Initialize git in that direcory and config your username, email
3)In the directory "gitc1" create a file with name "gitext" 
4)Add the line "git ins, cs, commits" into that file then save and exit
5)now stage the changes and commit the file with commit message as "initial commit"
SREENSHOT: type command "git log --oneline" and send ss

